<div class="titlewrap">
    <img src="NexusInc.png" alt="Nexus Header" style="width:100%; border-radius:4px; margin-bottom:20px; border: 1px solid #333;">
   
    ...
<div class="tlogo">Nexus Platform Inc. &mdash; Internal Systems</div>
<div class="tmain">THE FEED<br>MACHINE</div>
<div class="tsub">You have just been promoted to Product Manager of Personalization at Nexus &mdash; a fast-growing content platform with 200 million monthly users. The investor demo is in five days. Four decisions stand between you and the pitch.</div>
<div class="trole">You are: Jordan Mercer &mdash; PM, Personalization</div>

<div class="term"><span class="tlabel">// SYSTEM NOTICE &mdash; CONFIDENTIAL</span>Each decision you make will shift four live metrics: Engagement, Revenue, User Trust, and User Well-being. You cannot maximize all four simultaneously. The tradeoffs are real &mdash; modeled on documented practices inside actual platforms.

There are no correct answers. There are only choices, and what follows them.</div>

[[ Begin &rarr; |Title Start]]
</div>


:: Title Start {"position":"275,25","size":"100,100"}
<div class="titlewrap">
<div class="tlogo">Background Briefing</div>
<h1>Who Is Jordan Mercer?</h1>

<p>You joined Nexus eighteen months ago as a mid-level product analyst. Last week you were promoted &mdash; not because you asked for it, but because your predecessor, Marcus Webb, resigned without explanation. His desk was cleared the same afternoon.</p>

<p>Nexus serves 200 million monthly active users. Its personalization engine drives 78% of total content consumption on the platform. You did not build this system. You inherited it.</p>

<p>The platform runs on what researcher Shoshana Zuboff calls <em>behavioral surplus</em> &mdash; data extracted beyond what is needed to serve users, repurposed to predict and shape their future behavior. Every click, pause, hover, and scroll is logged. The system does not just respond to users' interests. It anticipates and, in subtle ways, produces them.</p>

<p>You have five days until the investor demo. Four decisions to make. The company is watching.</p>

<div class="rsrc"><span class="rtag">Research Context &mdash; Zuboff (2019)</span>Zuboff's concept of behavioral surplus describes how platforms extract data beyond service delivery to predict and modify future behavior. This logic &mdash; collect everything, optimize for engagement &mdash; is the foundation of the system you are now responsible for.</div>

[[ Enter the office &rarr; |Round 1 Intro]]
</div>


:: StoryStylesheet [stylesheet]
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Mono:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=DM+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..40,300;0,9..40,400;0,9..40,600;1,9..40,300&display=swap');

:root {
  --bg:        #080b12;
  --bg2:       #0e1320;
  --bg3:       #161d2e;
  --border:    #1f2d47;
  --accent:    #3b82f6;
  --accent2:   #34d399;
  --danger:    #f87171;
  --warn:      #fbbf24;
  --muted:     #94a3b8;
  --bright:    #f1f5f9;
  --text:      #cbd5e1;
  --eng:       #60a5fa;
  --rev:       #a78bfa;
  --trust:     #34d399;
  --wb:        #fb923c;
  --mono:      'Space Mono', monospace;
  --sans:      'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  --r:         8px;
}

*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

html, body {
  background: var(--bg) !important;
  color: var(--text);
  font-family: var(--sans);
  font-size: 16px;
  line-height: 1.75;
  min-height: 100vh;
}

body::after {
  content: '';
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  background: repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, transparent, transparent 3px, rgba(0,0,0,0.04) 3px, rgba(0,0,0,0.04) 4px);
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 9000;
}

body::before {
  content: '';
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  background-image:
    linear-gradient(rgba(59,130,246,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(59,130,246,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 40px 40px;
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 0;
}

#story, tw-story {
  background: var(--bg) !important;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}

tw-passage {
  display: block;
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 40px 28px 100px;
}

h1, h2, h3 {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  color: var(--bright);
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
}
h1 { font-size: 1.9rem; line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 0.5em; }
h2 { font-size: 1.15rem; margin-bottom: 0.8em; color: var(--accent); }
h3 { font-size: 0.8rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 0.5em; }
p  { margin-bottom: 1.1em; }
em { color: var(--accent2); font-style: italic; }
strong { color: var(--bright); font-weight: 600; }

tw-link, tw-link:visited {
  display: block;
  background: var(--bg3);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
  color: var(--bright) !important;
  font-family: var(--sans);
  font-size: 0.94rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  padding: 15px 20px;
  margin: 10px 0;
  border-radius: var(--r);
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.15s ease;
  text-decoration: none !important;
  line-height: 1.5;
}
tw-link:hover {
  background: #1c2840;
  border-left-color: var(--accent2);
  color: var(--accent2) !important;
  transform: translateX(5px);
  box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(59,130,246,0.15);
}

.db {
  background: var(--bg2);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--r);
  padding: 18px 22px;
  margin: 24px 0;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 0.8rem;
}
.dbtitle {
  color: var(--muted);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  margin-bottom: 14px;
  padding-bottom: 10px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.mr { margin-bottom: 12px; }
.ml { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 5px; }
.mn { color: var(--muted); }
.mv { color: var(--bright); font-weight: 700; }
.mb { height: 5px; background: var(--border); border-radius: 99px; overflow: hidden; }
.mf { height: 100%; border-radius: 99px; }
.fe { background: var(--eng); }
.fr { background: var(--rev); }
.ft { background: var(--trust); }
.fw { background: var(--wb); }

.inbox { margin: 22px 0; }
.mc {
  background: var(--bg2);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--r);
  padding: 15px 18px;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  font-size: 0.88rem;
}
.mfrom { font-family: var(--mono); color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.72rem; margin-bottom: 4px; }
.msubj { font-weight: 600; color: var(--bright); margin-bottom: 7px; font-size: 0.9rem; }
.mbody { color: var(--text); line-height: 1.65; }
.mu  { border-left: 3px solid var(--danger); }
.mg  { border-left: 3px solid var(--accent2); }
.mw  { border-left: 3px solid var(--warn); }
.mn2 { border-left: 3px solid var(--border); }

.term {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  background: #040609;
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--r);
  padding: 18px 20px;
  color: var(--accent2);
  margin: 18px 0;
  white-space: pre-wrap;
  line-height: 1.7;
}
.term .tlabel {
  color: var(--muted);
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
}

.divider { border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); margin: 26px 0; }

.titlewrap {
  min-height: 95vh;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: 40px 0 20px;
}
.tlogo {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  color: var(--accent);
  letter-spacing: 0.22em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
.tmain {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 8vw, 4.4rem);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--bright);
  line-height: 1.0;
  letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.tsub {
  font-size: 1rem;
  color: var(--muted);
  max-width: 500px;
  margin-bottom: 14px;
  line-height: 1.7;
  font-weight: 300;
}
.trole {
  display: inline-block;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 0.72rem;
  background: rgba(59,130,246,0.1);
  border: 1px solid var(--accent);
  color: var(--accent);
  padding: 4px 12px;
  border-radius: 99px;
  margin-bottom: 36px;
}

.badge {
  display: inline-block;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  background: rgba(59,130,246,0.08);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  color: var(--muted);
  padding: 3px 10px;
  border-radius: 99px;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 22px;
}

.prog {
  display: flex;
  gap: 5px;
  margin-bottom: 30px;
  align-items: center;
}
.pip       { height: 3px; flex: 1; border-radius: 99px; background: var(--border); }
.pipdone   { background: var(--accent); }
.pipactive { background: var(--accent2); }
.proglabel {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 0.65rem;
  color: var(--muted);
  white-space: nowrap;
  margin-left: 8px;
}

.clabel {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  color: var(--muted);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  margin-top: 4px;
}

.endwrap { padding: 20px 0 40px; }
.endtitle {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 2rem;
  color: var(--bright);
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  line-height: 1.1;
}
.endtag {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 0.72rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  margin-bottom: 26px;
  display: block;
}
.tagbad  { color: var(--danger); }
.tagmid  { color: var(--warn); }
.taggood { color: var(--accent2); }

.fgrid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 10px;
  margin: 26px 0;
}
.fbox {
  background: var(--bg2);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--r);
  padding: 16px;
  font-family: var(--mono);
  text-align: center;
}
.fval { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--bright); }
.flbl { font-size: 0.68rem; color: var(--muted); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-top: 3px; }

.rsrc {
  background: rgba(59,130,246,0.06);
  border: 1px solid rgba(59,130,246,0.2);
  border-radius: var(--r);
  padding: 14px 18px;
  margin: 18px 0;
  font-size: 0.84rem;
  color: var(--text);
  line-height: 1.65;
}
.rsrc .rtag {
  font-family: var(--mono);
  font-size: 0.68rem;
  color: var(--accent);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}

.dbox {
  background: var(--bg2);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: var(--r);
  padding: 13px 18px;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  font-size: 0.86rem;
}
.dround  { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 4px; }
.dchoice { color: var(--bright); font-weight: 600; }

@media (max-width: 520px) {
  tw-passage { padding: 20px 16px 60px; }
  .tmain { font-size: 2.4rem; }
}